    "The model was trained using MD simulation data of intrinsically disordered peptides of varying lengths or α-synuclein.",
    "idpGAN was successful in predicting sequence-dependent ensembles for sequences of peptides not present in the training set, demonstrating transferability beyond the limited training data (Janson et al. 2023).",
